---
description: Content/mod rules — safe zone for non-programmers
globs: ["mods/**"]
---
- Content is JSON + assets only. Copy an existing def of the same type as a template.
- Every def needs a namespaced id: "core:snake_case_name". IDs are permanent —
  never rename one that's been merged (saves reference them).
- Reference sprites by manifest KEY. Add the key to assets/manifest.json in the
  same PR. Placeholder sprite key "placeholder" is allowed and encouraged early.
- Prefer tags over item lists in recipes and effects.
- Run `npm run validate` before committing — it checks every def against its schema
  and every asset reference against manifests. A red validate = do not commit.
- Sprites: 16px grid, snake_case.png, correct category folder.
